article_id:2343,category_name:News,title_name:Gala Dragalia Remix Is Now Live!,image_path:,message:<div>Gala Dragalia Remix started on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1626328800"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>What are Gala Dragalia and Gala Dragalia Remix?</div><div>The initial appearance rate for 5★ adventurers and dragons is boosted to 6%, which is up from the standard 4%! If you get a 5★ summon or 5★ featured summon, the appearance rate will return to the initial 6%.</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">The Scratch-A-Thon Summon that is live at the same time does not include the newly added limited-time featured adventurers or dragons appearing in this showcase.</span></div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">Adventurers added in past Gala Dragalia summon showcases may appear in this summon showcase as well. For information about which adventurers may appear, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Appearance Rates and check the Appearance Rates section.</span></div><div><br></div><div>Newly added limited-time featured adventurers:</div><div>5★ Summer Ieyasu (water/sword)</div><div>5★ Summer Mitsuhide (flame/dagger)</div><div><br></div><div>Newly added limited-time featured dragon:</div><div>5★ Summer Marishiten (water)</div><div><br></div><div>Featured adventurer from past Gala Dragalia summon showcases:</div><div>5★ Gala Leonidas (flame/rapid-fire manacaster)</div><div><br></div><div>Gala Dragalia Remix appearance rates:</div><div>5★ total: 6.00%</div><div>5★ featured total: 2.30% (Adventurers: 1.50%, Dragons: 0.80%)</div><div>5★ standard total: 3.70% (Adventurers: 1.50%, Dragons: 2.20%)</div><div>4★ standard total: 16.00% (Adventurers: 8.55%, Dragons: 7.45%)</div><div>3★ standard total: 78.00% (Adventurers: 47.00%, Dragons: 31.00%)</div><div><br></div><div>Gala Dragalia Remix event duration:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1626328800"></span> to <span class="local_da